records.name: Pullman Maldives All-inclusive Resort

descriptions.direction: Located in Maamutaa Island, Pullman Maldives Resort is on a private beach. Kooddoo Harbor and Falhumaafushi Dock are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Hadahaa Beach and Kodahuttaa Island. Looking to get your feet wet? Water tubing and swimming adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Pullman Maldives Maamutaa, a generous five-star all-inclusive resort, offers a 55-minute flight from Male to Kooddoo Airport, followed by a 15-minute speedboat ride. Set on 18 hectares of tropical paradise, it features 122 villas and suites, including unique underwater options. Guests enjoy three restaurants, three bars, water sports and diving, fitness activities, and The Pullman Spa. Year-round events ensure inspiration and fun, blending adrenaline-filled adventures with serene relaxation.
